{"id":484,"date":"2019-03-01T22:34:40","date_gmt":"2019-03-01T22:34:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/?page_id=484"},"modified":"2019-03-06T19:10:44","modified_gmt":"2019-03-06T19:10:44","slug":"adidas-inbox-first","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/adidas-inbox-first\/","title":{"rendered":"Adidas: Inbox First"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2>How do you keep your biggest fans up to date without social media algorithms getting in the way?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3710\" height=\"2170\" src=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas: Inbox First - is an EDM CRM program designed to go direct to out biggest fans. It was created to stop social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram and Twitter from using tweaks to their algorithm from disintermediating us from our fans. It uses the latest Adidas collaborations, from Run DMC to Jeremy Scott to do that. I was creative director on this campaign.\" class=\"wp-image-489\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2.jpg 3710w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2-300x175.jpg 300w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2-768x449.jpg 768w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2-1024x599.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-Insitu-V2-2-1568x917.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3710px) 100vw, 3710px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"6635\" src=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas: Inbox First - is an EDM CRM program designed to go direct to out biggest fans. It was created to stop social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram and Twitter from using tweaks to their algorithm from disintermediating us from our fans. It uses the latest Adidas collaborations, from Run DMC to Jeremy Scott to do that. I was creative director on this campaign.\" class=\"wp-image-490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1-90x300.jpg 90w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1-768x2548.jpg 768w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1-309x1024.jpg 309w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V1-1568x5202.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1666\" height=\"6635\" src=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-491\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2.jpg 1666w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2-75x300.jpg 75w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2-768x3059.jpg 768w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2-257x1024.jpg 257w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Misc-Adidas-EDMs-V2-1568x6245.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1666px) 100vw, 1666px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p><strong>You do it with an old-school email strategy to hit up people with the latest stuff to hit Adidas in Australia.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>And you make sure that you only give them content and products \nthey\u2019re interested in. You also need to trust your data and the insights\n they give